<li id="cite_note-41"><b><a href="#cite_ref-41" title="">^</a></b> Goodchild 2005, p. 36</li>
<li id="cite_note-42"><b><a href="#cite_ref-42" title="">^</a></b> This quote has been primarily attributed to Rabi in many news sources (see, e.g., McKie, Robin, <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/reviews/scienceandnature/0,6121,1207700,00.html" class="external text" title="http://books.guardian.co.uk/reviews/scienceandnature/0,6121,1207700,00.html" rel="nofollow">Megaton megalomaniac</a>, <i>The Observer</i>, May 2, 2004), but it has also in a few reputable sources been attributed to Hans Bethe (i.e. in the <a href="http://www.brotherhoodofthebomb.com/bhbmedia/notes_epilogue.doc" class="external text" title="http://www.brotherhoodofthebomb.com/bhbmedia/notes_epilogue.doc" rel="nofollow">notes to the Epilogue in Herken 2002</a>, note 40).</li>
<li id="cite_note-MOF-43">^ <a href="#cite_ref-MOF_43-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-MOF_43-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.medaloffreedom.com/EdwardTeller.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.medaloffreedom.com/EdwardTeller.htm" rel="nofollow">"Presidential Medal of Freedom Recipient Dr. Edward Teller"</a>. Presidential Medal of Freedom<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.medaloffreedom.com/EdwardTeller.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.medaloffreedom.com/EdwardTeller.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.medaloffreedom.com/EdwardTeller.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-11-28</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Presidential+Medal+of+Freedom+Recipient+Dr.+Edward+Teller&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Presidential+Medal+of+Freedom&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.medaloffreedom.com%2FEdwardTeller.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Edward_Teller"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-44"><b><a href="#cite_ref-44" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.time.com/time/subscriber/personoftheyear/archive/stories/1960.html" class="external text" title="http://www.time.com/time/subscriber/personoftheyear/archive/stories/1960.html" rel="nofollow">"Time Person of the year, 1960: U.S. Scientists"</a>. <i>Time</i> magazine. January 2, 1961<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.time.com/time/subscriber/personoftheyear/archive/stories/1960.html" class="external free" title="http://www.time.com/time/subscriber/personoftheyear/archive/stories/1960.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.time.com/time/subscriber/personoftheyear/archive/stories/1960.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-11-28</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Time+Person+of+the+year%2C+1960%3A+U.S.+Scientists&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=January+2%2C+1961&amp;rft.pub=%27%27Time%27%27+magazine&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.time.com%2Ftime%2Fsubscriber%2Fpersonoftheyear%2Farchive%2Fstories%2F1960.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Edward_Teller"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-45"><b><a href="#cite_ref-45" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.nasa.gov/centers/ames/pdf/80021main_112700Astrogram.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.nasa.gov/centers/ames/pdf/80021main_112700Astrogram.pdf" rel="nofollow">"The Ames Astrogram: Teller visits Ames"</a> (PDF). NASA. November 27, 2000. p. 6<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.nasa.gov/centers/ames/pdf/80021main_112700Astrogram.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.nasa.gov/centers/ames/pdf/80021main_112700Astrogram.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.nasa.gov/centers/ames/pdf/80021main_112700Astrogram.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-11-28</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Ames+Astrogram%3A+Teller+visits+Ames&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=November+27%2C+2000&amp;rft.pages=p.+6&amp;rft.pub=NASA&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fcenters%2Fames%2Fpdf%2F80021main_112700Astrogram.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Edward_Teller"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
