i/Isidor_Isaac_Rabi" title="Isidor Isaac Rabi">Isidor Rabi</a> / <a href="/wiki/Emilio_G._Segr%C3%A8" title="Emilio G. Segrè">Emilio Segrè</a> / <a href="/wiki/William_Shockley" title="William Shockley">William Shockley</a> / <strong class="selflink">Edward Teller</strong> / <a href="/wiki/Charles_Hard_Townes" title="Charles Hard Townes">Charles Townes</a> / <a href="/wiki/James_Van_Allen" title="James Van Allen">James Van Allen</a> / <a href="/wiki/Robert_Burns_Woodward" title="Robert Burns Woodward">Robert Woodward</a> (1960)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/John_F._Kennedy" title="John F. Kennedy">John F. Kennedy</a> (1961)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Pope_John_XXIII" title="Pope John XXIII">Pope John XXIII</a> (1962)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Martin_Luther_King,_Jr." title="Martin Luther King, Jr.">Martin Luther King, Jr.</a> (1963)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Lyndon_B._Johnson" title="Lyndon B. Johnson">Lyndon B. Johnson</a> (1964)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/William_Westmoreland" title="William Westmoreland">William Westmoreland</a> (1965)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Baby_boomer" title="Baby boomer" class="mw-redirect">The Generation Twenty-Five and Under</a> (1966)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Lyndon_B._Johnson" title="Lyndon B. Johnson">Lyndon B. Johnson</a> (1967)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Apollo_8" title="Apollo 8">The Apollo 8 Astronauts</a>: <a href="/wiki/William_Anders" title="William Anders">William Anders</a> / <a href="/wiki/Frank_Borman" title="Frank Borman">Frank Borman</a> / <a href="/wiki/Jim_Lovell" title="Jim Lovell">Jim Lovell</a> (1968)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Middle_America_(United_States)" title="Middle America (United States)" class="mw-redirect